title: Get Queue
description: Gets a queue, good for see what's the current music and see what's next.
observations:
This is a function from the [createPlayer](https://github.com/ThePedroo/FastLink/tree/main/docs/createPlayer.md)/[getPlayer](https://github.com/ThePedroo/FastLink/tree/main/docs/getPlayer.md) functions. You **will** need one of them for use this function.

This function is ignored if the option for the FastLink handle the Queue it's not set for true. See [connectNode](https://github.com/ThePedroo/FastLink/tree/main/docs/connectNode.md) options for enable it.
